 ('90', '90', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This is a call to action', 'Kent, OH 44240', '330.672.7300', 'info@ideabasekent.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Website Designed and Developed By IdeaBase in Kent, OH.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Copyright 2015 IdeaBase</p>', '<p>Opened in 2009, IdeaBase, formerly the Tannery, was the brainchild of Jim Gaudino, the former and founding dean of the College of Communication and Information. IdeaBase is now a thriving design agency where top-performing from Kent State University assemble to solve problems for clients within and outside of the university.</p>', 'Let\'s make something great together.', '<p>Be a part of something big. Partner with our team of student designers on your next design initiative and be a part of our educational mission. Get in touch today by contacting Kristin Dowling, Business Development Manager, via email, phone, or by completing the form below:</p>', 'Get in touch today.', NULL, '138 E. Main Street, Suite 203', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2015-09-29 14:19:11', '2016-01-04 02:23:11', '2b55ea27-2a40-4f98-bcde-68e8a652d03d'),
