 ('311', '316', 'en_us', 'Callie Sullivan', NULL, 'UX Designer', 'csullivan@ideabasekent.com', '', '<p>Callie received her Bachelor’s degree in English from UW-Madison and is currently pursuing her Master’s degree in User Experience Design through Kent State University, where she will graduate in August of 2016.&nbsp;She is dually employed by IdeaBase, as well as a pharmacy benefit management company called Navitus based out of Madison, Wisconsin. At Navitus, Callie works as a Marketing Analyst and is part of the organization’s Web team, assisting primarily on content creation and organization for both the company’s internal and external sites. works in the Marketing department of a pharmacy benefit management company called Navitus based out of Madison, Wisconsin. At IdeaBase, Callie has worked on several projects&mdash;including the State Library of Ohio redesign, the design of the ICE Consulting website, and the redesign of the IdeaBase website&mdash;as the lead Content Strategist and Information Architect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>When Callie’s not eating, sleeping and breathing UX, she’s pursuing her other passions, which include music, the French language, travel and cheese plates.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'B.A. English, M.S. User Experience Design Graduate Student', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sullivan', 'Callie ', '0', NULL, '2015-12-29 15:39:30', '2016-01-14 19:17:00', 'fd171b5e-9de7-4b06-b5da-57f31f6c186b'),
