 ('334', '339', 'en_us', 'Beyond the Beans: Life of a Coffee Roaster and User Experience Designer: Christopher Uhler', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>My name is Chris Uhler and I’m a user experience designer at IdeaBase. I’m also a graduate student in Kent State’s user experience design program.<br>IdeaBase has been a great opportunity for gaining real-world experience. Personally, I’ve been learning a ton from my manager Chris Hallahan. He is a super awesome resource, and it’s truly rewarding to be able to work on a project the whole way through.<br>Before I started at IdeaBase in March, I actually had no idea this place even existed until my co-worker at Bent Tree Coffee Roasters told me about it. I’ve been working at Bent Tree (also here in Kent) for two years as a Production Manager, but I’m glad I found out about IdeaBase because it’s a great starting point for my future in the User Experience Design field.<br>My main client right now is Northeast Ohio Medical University. I am working on a competitive analysis for them in support of their future website redesign. A competitive analysis is basically the process of looking at similar websites and analyzing their strengths and weaknesses. I’ve also created and sent out a survey to get feedback on the current site, and I’ll be analyzing the data when the survey closes.<br>I stay super busy with work and school, but in my spare time I enjoy photography, home brewing, and my motorcycle. Recently, I made a Kolsch brew, which is a light, sweet beer. I think it turned out pretty well. I needed a break from the heavy stuff, and this was a nice alternative.<br>Right now, I’m just super excited to get married in the fall. My fiancé and I have been together about 5 years. We actually met at Kent State, and have been together ever since.<br>Overall, I am just excited for the experience at IdeaBase. I know I will be able to learn a lot here and can use this experience as a good foundation for my future.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '2015-12-29 19:15:59', '2015-12-29 19:15:59', 'bb1ae383-e4a7-434d-8444-e9dc34316b22'),
