 ('385', '390', 'en_us', 'Pamela Grimm, Ph.D.', NULL, 'Associate Professor, Marketing Chair', '', '', '<p>Dr. Grimm joined Kent State University in 1992 as an Associate Professor. She is currently an Associate Professor and Chair of the Department of Marketing and Entrepreneurship. She worked in Advertising before pursuing and completing her doctorate in Marketing at the State University of New York at Buffalo. Her research interests are in consumer behavior, specifically motivation and information search, advertising and celebrity endorsements. Dr. Grimm has been a participant in the Advertising Education Foundation’s Faculty Internship program and has received several teaching awards. Courses she has taught include Marketing, Consumer Behavior, Advertising and Internet Marketing at the Undergraduate level and Marketing Management at the Graduate level. Dr. Grimm has also been a faculty member in the Executive MBA program, teaching the International Business Experience.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Grimm, Ph.D.', 'Pamela', '0', NULL, '2016-01-05 19:09:07', '2016-01-05 19:09:07', '404fcb8c-a12f-43ff-ae73-bd06fccc3c69'),
